text: I attended Escape back in 2012, it is a great place to learn comp. I'm now a 2D lead compositor at Electric Theatre Collective. Feel free to ping me any questions you have and share your work. I'm always happy to help. How have you found the course so far?

The course has been really good, I’ve enjoyed all the projects that I have worked on so far. And I’m looking forward to my upcoming final group project starting soon.
Would you be able to share some feedback on one of my projects I’m currently working on please?
It is a keying shot in which I have made a DMP background of a jungle.
I’m trying to stylize the shot to be dramatic referencing shots from films like Jumanji.
